node.text: As the owner of @cote_nyc and @cotemiami, @simonkimnyc is always on the go, from Seoul, to New York, to Las Vegas. The audacious restaurateur needs an equally audacious vehicle, like a #Maserati Ghibli Trofeo, to keep up. Swipe to tour the Ghibli Trofeo. #TheArtofFast #Maserati @worldredeye @thecollectionfl. #Drive305

Maserati meets Fragment.
A work of art that blazed an audacious trail from Modena to Tokyo.
Relive the journey of the Ghibli Operanera from its conception to reveal on the streets of Harajuku.
